        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer210232513" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13870312228357903892">This is great collection of 7 classic ghost stories. Most relate to traveling scholars and their ghostly encounters. My only complaint is that many of these stories are very similar. Out of the 7, the story Number 13 is my favorite. This is a nice quick read if you are the mood for a few really good ghost stories. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

